-- Office Depot sees erosion of sales, earnings
-- 
-- Wed Dec 12, 2007 9:00am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/12/12/us-officedepot-outlook-idUSWNAS437220071212

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Office supplies retailer Office Depot Inc ( ODP.N ) on Wednesday said it sees sales and earnings continuing to erode in the fourth quarter due to housing-related struggles in some of its key markets. 

 The company also said its expects vendor program support levels to be about $70 million lower than last year. (Reporting by  Justin Grant , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)